<view class="page explore-page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="hero-visual">
      <view class="hero-glass">
        <view class="hero-glass-head"></view>
        <view class="hero-glass-fill"></view>
        <view class="hero-glass-line"></view>
      </view>
      <view class="hero-ring hero-ring-one"></view>
      <view class="hero-ring hero-ring-two"></view>
      <view class="hero-spark hero-spark-one"></view>
      <view class="hero-spark hero-spark-two"></view>
    </view>
    <view class="hero-copy">
      <text class="page-title">精酿风格指南</text>
      <text class="page-subtitle">从 BJCP 2021 标准到市场高频叫法，用大类、风格与快速搜索建立一张更清晰的味觉坐标。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="hero-stats">
      <view wx:for="{{overviewStats}}" wx:key="label" class="hero-stat">
        <text class="hero-stat-value">{{item.value}}</text>
        <text class="hero-stat-label">{{item.label}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="search-entry" hover-class="entry-hover" hover-stay-time="80" bindtap="openSearch">
      <view class="search-copy">
        <text class="search-label">搜索编号 / 中文 / English</text>
        <text class="search-hint">例如 21A、浑浊、West Coast IPA</text>
      </view>
      <text class="search-entry-icon">›</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-switch">
    <view
      wx:for="{{sectionTabs}}"
      wx:key="id"
      class="section-tab {{activeSection === item.id ? 'section-tab-active' : ''}}"
      data-section-id="{{item.id}}"
      hover-class="tab-hover"
      hover-stay-time="80"
      bindtap="switchSection"
    >
      <text>{{item.label}}</text>
      <text>{{item.countLabel}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{activeSection === 'bjcp'}}" class="section-panel">
    <view class="section-head">
      <text>风格大类</text>
      <text>{{groups.length}} 个入口</text>
    </view>

    <view class="group-grid">
      <view
        wx:for="{{groups}}"
        wx:for-index="index"
        wx:key="id"
        class="group-card"
        style="border-left-color: {{item.color}}"
        data-group-id="{{item.id}}"
        hover-class="card-hover"
        hover-stay-time="80"
        bindtap="openGroup"
      >
        <view class="group-card-glow" style="background: {{item.color}}"></view>
        <view class="group-card-orbit" style="border-color: {{item.color}}"></view>
        <view class="group-card-scan" style="background: {{item.color}}"></view>
        <view class="group-card-bar" style="background: {{item.color}}"></view>
        <view class="group-card-main">
          <view class="group-code-pill">
            <text class="group-index">0{{index + 1}}</text>
            <view class="group-code-dot" style="background: {{item.color}}"></view>
          </view>
          <text class="group-name">{{item.name}}</text>
          <text class="group-en">{{item.nameEn}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="group-card-meta">
          <view class="meta-block">
            <text class="meta-value">{{item.categoryCount}}</text>
            <text class="meta-label">类别</text>
          </view>
          <view class="meta-block">
            <text class="meta-value">{{item.styleCount}}</text>
            <text class="meta-label">风格</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:else class="section-panel">
    <view class="section-head">
      <text>市场扩展风格</text>
      <text>{{extensionGroups.length}} 组</text>
    </view>

    <view class="extension-intro">
      <text>BA/WBC/GABF 体系中常见、但 BJCP 未独立编号的市场风格。先认识市场叫法，再回到近似 BJCP 入口继续学习。</text>
    </view>

    <view class="group-grid">
      <view
        wx:for="{{extensionGroups}}"
        wx:for-index="index"
        wx:key="id"
        class="group-card extension-group-card"
        style="border-left-color: {{item.color}}"
        data-group-id="{{item.id}}"
        hover-class="card-hover"
        hover-stay-time="80"
        bindtap="openExtensionGroup"
      >
        <view class="group-card-glow" style="background: {{item.color}}"></view>
        <view class="group-card-orbit" style="border-color: {{item.color}}"></view>
        <view class="group-card-scan" style="background: {{item.color}}"></view>
        <view class="group-card-bar" style="background: {{item.color}}"></view>
        <view class="group-card-main">
          <view class="group-code-pill">
            <text class="group-index">M{{index + 1}}</text>
            <view class="group-code-dot" style="background: {{item.color}}"></view>
          </view>
          <text class="group-name">{{item.name}}</text>
          <text class="group-en">{{item.nameEn}}</text>
          <text class="extension-summary">{{item.summary}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="group-card-meta">
          <view class="meta-block">
            <text class="meta-value">{{item.styleCount}}</text>
            <text class="meta-label">风格</text>
          </view>
          <text class="meta-tag">扩展</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-head">
    <text>快速入口</text>
    <text>IPA</text>
  </view>

  <scroll-view scroll-x class="featured-strip">
    <view
      wx:for="{{featured}}"
      wx:key="id"
      class="style-chip-card"
      style="border-top-color: {{item.color}}"
      data-style-id="{{item.id}}"
      data-item-kind="{{item.kind}}"
      hover-class="chip-hover"
      hover-stay-time="80"
      bindtap="openStyle"
    >
      <text class="style-code" wx:if="{{item.kind !== 'extension'}}">{{item.code}}</text>
      <text class="style-code" wx:else>扩展</text>
      <text class="style-name">{{item.displayName}}</text>
      <text class="style-en">{{item.name_en}}</text>
    </view>
  </scroll-view>
</view>
